        <p>You can also access the data processed in accordance with the KVKK in detail by clicking on the "Privacy Notice (Clarification Text)".</p>

        <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">PURPOSES AND LEGAL REASONS FOR PROCESSING PERSONAL DATA</h3>
